CustomField.description: Sets the % Completed Group according to % Completed
CustomField.formula: IF( CLZV6BP__CLZ_PercentCompleted__c < 25/100,"<25%", IF(CLZV6BP__CLZ_PercentCompleted__c <= 50/100 && CLZV6BP__CLZ_PercentCompleted__c >= 26/100, "26% to 50%", IF(CLZV6BP__CLZ_PercentCompleted__c <= 75/100 && CLZV6BP__CLZ_PercentCompleted__c >= 51/100, "51% to 75%", IF(CLZV6BP__CLZ_PercentCompleted__c <= 100/100&& CLZV6BP__CLZ_PercentCompleted__c >= 76/100, "76% to 100%", null) ) ))
CustomField.label: % Complete Group
